20media%20partnerships%20and%20a%20%241%20billion%20funding%20round.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fkalshi-polymarket-fanduel-draftkings-sports-betting-gambling-2025-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EKalshi's%20CEO%3C%2Fa%3E%20says%20his%20company's%20rivalry%20with%20Polymarket%20has%20parallels%20to%20two%20sets%20of%20sporting%20legends.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20episode%20of%20the%20%26quot%3B20VC%26quot%3B%20podcast%20released%20on%20Monday%2C%20Tarek%20Mansour%20explained%20how%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsports-betting-odds-gambling-lines-memecoins-prediction-markets-polymarket-stocks-2024-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eprediction%20market%20rival%20Polymarket%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20encouraged%20his%20company%20to%20work%20harder.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhat%20I'm%20learning%20over%20time%20is%20that%20an%20industry%20truly%20becomes%20an%20industry%20when%20there's%20a%20rivalry%2C%20because%20that%20rivalry%20will%20push%20you%20beyond%20the%20limits%20of%20what%20you%20thought%20you%20could%20get%20to%2C%26quot%3B%20Mansour%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20compared%20the%20companies%20to%20National%20Football%20League%20quarterbacks%20Tom%20Brady%20and%20Eli%20Manning.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20Tom%20Brady%20kind%20of%20reflected%20on%20that%20back%20in%20the%20day%2C%20he's%20like%2C%20'You%20know%2C%20we%20were%20like%20the%20most%20ferocious%20on%20the%20field%2C%20and%20we%20fought%20each%20other%2C'%26quot%3B%20Mansour%20said.%20%26quot%3BBut%20then%20over%20time%2C%20he%20became%20grateful%20for%20that%20because%20he%20realized%20that%20without%20Manning%20being%20in%20there%20and%20vice%20versa%2C%20he%20would%20have%20never%20achieved%20what%20he%20achieved.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20that's%20happening%20in%20prediction%20markets%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKalshi%2C%20founded%20in%202018%2C%20lets%20users%20bet%20on%20the%20outcome%20of%20events%20such%20as%20elections%2C%20sports%20matches%2C%20and%20economic%20indicators.%20Last%20week%2C%20it%20announced%20partnerships%20with%20media%20giants%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fkalshi-cnbc-deal-cnn-data-integration-partnership-2025-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ECNN%20and%20CNBC%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20said%20that%20it%20raised%20%241%20billion%20at%20a%20valuation%20of%20%2411%20billion.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPolymarket%2C%20its%20blockchain-enabled%20competitor%2C%20was%20founded%20in%202020%20and%20offers%20similar%20services.%20It%20was%20last%20valued%20at%20%2413.5%20billion%20in%20November%2C%20per%20PitchBook.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20popularity%20of%20prediction%20platforms%20has%20exploded%20since%20a%20legal%20victory%20for%20Kalshi%20in%20the%20US%20last%20fall.%20Now%2C%20users%20can%20bet%20on%20questions%20ranging%20from%20the%20popularity%20of%20Labubu%20dolls%20to%20Elon%20Musk's%20net%20worth.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELast%20year%2C%20Mansour%20said%20in%20an%20interview%20that%20his%20employees%20asked%20social%20media%20influencers%20to%20promote%20memes%20about%20an%20FBI%20raid%20on%20the%20home%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpolymarket-sees-valuation-skyrocket-in-new-funding-round-2025-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EPolymarket%20CEO%20Shayne%20Coplan%3C%2Fa%3E.%20On%20Monday's%20podcast%2C%20Mansour%20called%20the%20move%20a%20%26quot%3Bmistake%26quot%3B%20and%20said%20he%20%26quot%3Bmade%20clear%20to%20the%20team%3A%20'Don't%20ever%20do%20this%20again.'%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMansour%20also%20compared%20the%20two%20companies%20to%20soccer%20stars%20Lionel%20Messi%20and%20Cristiano%20Ronaldo%2C%20and%20said%20that%20it%20was%20not%20a%20coincidence%20that%20the%20two%20%26quot%3Bgreatest%26quot%3B%20players%20exist%20in%20the%20same%20era.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWithout%20Polymarket%2C%20we%20wouldn't%20have%20pushed%20our%20marketing%20and%20pushe