s%20for%20heavy%20people%20have%20limited%20showroom%20availability%2C%20so%20look%20for%20sleep%20tests%20and%20trial%20periods.%20Usually%2C%20you'll%20be%20required%20to%20sleep%20on%20the%20mattress%20for%20at%20least%2030%20nights%2C%20and%20if%20it's%20not%20for%20you%2C%20you%20can%20send%20it%20back%20or%20have%20it%20donated%20for%20a%20replacement%20or%20refund.%20Each%20mattress%20on%20our%20list%20has%20%E2%80%94%20at%20least%20%E2%80%94%20a%20120-night%20warranty.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Chr%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%223834574e-1b7f-4f37-ad20-25b9d69db5f7%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22How%20we%20test%20the%20best%20mattresses%20for%20heavy%20people%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20we%20test%20the%20best%20mattresses%20for%20heavy%20people%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20notebook%20and%20pen%2C%20sparkling%20water%20can%2C%20thermometer%2C%20and%20ruler%20on%20the%20WinkBed%20Plus.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68790a6085e81483682e3077%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EI%20test%20heat%20dissipation%2C%20motion%20isolation%2C%20and%20edge%20support%20with%20my%20trusty%20infrared%20thermometer%2C%20ruler%2C%20and%20soda%20can.%3Cp%3EKinsley%20Searles%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20put%20each%20mattress%20through%20a%20rigorous%20testing%20process.%20Our%20testing%20procedures%20include%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EComfort%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EI%20slept%20on%20each%20mattress%20for%20at%20least%20three%20weeks%2C%20noting%20my%20comfort%20in%20each%20sleeping%20position%20as%20a%20plus-size%20person.%20I%20also%20share%20the%20bed%20with%20my%20partner%2C%20who%20falls%20in%20the%20weight%20range%20for%20a%20plus-size%20mattress%2C%20and%20gathered%20his%20thoughts%20and%20feedback%20as%20well.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EHeat%20dissipation%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EI%20measured%20the%20mattress's%20temperature%20with%20an%20infrared%20thermometer%20prior%20to%20going%20to%20sleep%2C%20immediately%20after%20getting%20up%2C%20and%20two%20minutes%20after%20leaving%20the%20bed.%20I%20repeated%20this%20process%20for%20seven%20mornings%20and%20recorded%20my%20findings%2C%20observing%20how%20cool%20the%20mattress%20stays%20and%20how%20quickly%20heat%20dissipates.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EEdge%20support%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EI%20sat%20on%20the%20edge%20of%20the%20mattress%20and%20measured%20how%20low%20it%20sank.%20I%20also%20lay%20on%20the%20edge%20of%20the%20mattress%20and%20slowly%20rolled%20off%2C%20noting%20the%20angle%20of%20my%20body%20when%20I%20fell.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EMotion%20isolation%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EI%20placed%20a%20soda%20can%20in%20the%20center%20of%20the%20bed%20and%20a%20vibrometer%20a%20foot%20away%2C%20then%20dropped%20a%2015-pound%20weight%20a%20foot%20away%20from%20the%20can%2010%20times.%20I%20observed%20how%20many%20times%20the%20can%20fell%20and%20the%20reading%20on%20the%20vibrometer.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Chr%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2204d856ee-178b-412b-99bf-155bee8d024d%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22FAQs%5C%22%3EBest%20mattress%20for%20heavy%20people%20FAQs%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Ch3%3EWhat%20is%20a%20plus-size%20mattress%3F%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EA%20plus-size%20mattress%20is%20a%20mattress%20specifically%20designed%20to%20support%20heavy%20people%20who%20typically%20weigh%20between%20250%20to%20500%20pounds.%20While%20it%20looks%20like%20a%20regular%20mattress%20from%20the%20outside%2C%20it%20uses%20stronger%2C%20more%20durable%20materials%20like%20high-gauge%20coils%20and%20high-density%20memory%20foams%20to%20prevent%20sagging%20and%20provide%20long-term%20support%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3EWhat%20type%20of%20mattress%20is%20best%20for%20plus-size%20sleepers%3F%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhome%2Fbest-hybrid-mattress%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EHybrid%