rating.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EIt%20is%20the%20first%20downgrade%20Tesla%20has%20received%20from%20Morgan%20Stanley%20since%20June%202023.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fstocks%2Ftsla-stock%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ETesla%3C%2Fa%3E%20stock%20got%20a%20downgrade%20on%20Monday%2C%20sending%20it%20tumbling%20as%20much%20as%204%25%20as%20Morgan%20Stanley%20lowered%20its%20recommendation%20for%20the%20first%20time%20since%202023.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMorgan%20Stanley's%20Andrew%20Percoco%20downgraded%20Tesla%20from%20an%20%26quot%3BOverweight%2FBuy%26quot%3B%20to%20an%20%26quot%3BEqual%20Weight%2FHold%26quot%3B%20rating.%20While%20he%20increased%20his%20price%20target%20to%20%24425%20per%20share%2C%20up%20from%20the%20previous%20%24410%2C%20his%20new%20target%20still%20implies%20about%203%25%20downside%20from%20levels%20late%20in%20the%20day%20on%20Monday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20analyst%20noted%20that%20he%20believes%20Tesla%20will%20continue%20making%20progress%20on%20key%20initiatives%2C%20particularly%20its%20advancements%20in%20full%20self-driving%20and%20robotic%20technology.%20However%2C%20he%20thinks%20investors%20should%20wait%20for%20a%20better%20entry%20point%2C%20as%20share%20prices%20remain%20highly%20valued%20and%20the%20company%20could%20encounter%20further%20challenges%20amid%20lower%20demand%20for%20electric%20cars.%20Percoco%20said%20the%20bank%20had%20lowered%20its%20outlook%20specifically%20for%20Tesla's%20auto%20business.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20a%20reflection%20of%20lower%20volume%20expectations%2C%20with%20a%2010.5%25%20reduction%20in%202026%20volumes%20and%2018.5%25%20reduction%20in%20cumulative%20deliveries%20through%202040%20due%20to%20our%20more%20cautious%20view%20on%20the%20pace%20of%20EV%20adoption%20in%20the%20US%20coupled%20with%20growing%20competition%20in%20global%20markets.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20been%20a%20volatile%20year%20for%20Tesla.%20After%20being