0regulatory%20certainty%20to%20close%2C%26quot%3B%20Ellison%20said.%20He%20called%20the%20deal%20%26quot%3Bpro-consumer%2C%20pro-creative%20talent%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Bpro-competition.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENetflix%20didn't%20respond%20to%20the%20hostile%20bid%20but%20has%20said%20that%20by%20combining%20its%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnetflix-to-buy-warner-bros-in-82-7-billion-megadeal-2025-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estreaming%20hits%20with%20WBD%3C%2Fa%3E's%20classic%20library%20and%20prestige%20HBO%20fare%2C%20it%20can%20supercharge%20its%20offering.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTogether%2C%20we%20can%20give%20audiences%20around%20the%20world%20even%20more%20value%20and%20choice%2C%20and%20get%20one%20step%20closer%20to%20being%20the%20most%20loved%20and%20the%20most%20valued%20entertainment%20company%2C%26quot%3B%20Netflix%20co-CEO%20Ted%20Sarandos%20said%20in%20announcing%20the%20deal%20Friday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHere's%20how%20the%20companies%20made%20their%20cases%20to%20various%20stakeholders%2C%20which%20include%20investors%2C%20employees%2C%20Hollywood%20talent%2C%20and%20regulators.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22184146d1-5847-47bc-a02d-e0701f2f7dbc%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EParamount%20Skydance%20says%20it%20is%20offering%20a%20higher%20price%20and%20more%20certainty%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EFinancials%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Paramount%20offered%20%2430%20per%20WBD%20share%20for%20all%20of%20WBD%2C%20compared%20to%20Netflix's%20offer%20of%20%2427.75%20per%20WBD%20share%20for%20its%20streaming%20and%20studios%20business%2C%20excluding%20its%20TV%20networks%2C%20such%20as%20CNN%20and%20TNT.%20While%20Netflix's%20offer%20was%20a%20mix%20of%20cash%20and%20stock%2C%20Ellison%20emphasized%20that%20Paramount's%20offer%20is%20all%20cash%2C%20and%20%2417.6%20billion%20more%20than%20the%20Netflix%20deal%2C%20an%20%2482.7%20billion%20offer%20that%20includes%20%2472%20billion%20in%20equity.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EApproval%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Ellison%20repeatedly%20argued%20that%20he's%20more%20likely%20to%20win%20regulatory%20approval%20than%20Netflix%20is.%20He%20said%20he%20anticipated%20approval%20coming%20in%20as%20little%20as%2012%20months.%20President%20Donald%20Trump%20said%20he'll%20be%20%26quot%3Binvolved%26quot%3B%20in%20evaluating%20the%20deal.%20Larry%20Ellison%20is%20a%20longtime%20ally%20of%20Trump%2C%20and%20the%20firm%20of%20Trump's%20son-in-law%2C%20Jared%20Kushner%2C%20is%20part%20of%20the%20Paramount%20offer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHollywood%20and%20consumers%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Ellison%20argued%20that%20the%20Paramount%20deal%20would%20be%20good%20for%20jobs%20and%20consumers.%20He%20said%20Paramount%20is%20committed%20to%20growing%20the%20film%20and%20TV%20output%20of%20both%20businesses%2C%20including%20a%20theatrical%20slate%20of%2030-plus%20releases%20a%20year.%20It's%20a%20pointed%20contrast%20with%20Netflix%2C%20whose%20preference%20for%20getting%20movies%20onto%20its%20streaming%20service%20quickly%20has%20created%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnetflix-explains-how-warner-bros-deal-with-impact-movie-strategy-2025-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efriction%20with%20the%20film%20industry%3C%2Fa%3E.%20(Netflix%20has%20said%20it%20would%20continue%20to%20release%20Warner%20Bros.%20movies%20in%20theaters.)%20Ellison%20said%20adding%20WBD%20would%20make%20Paramount%20a%20robust%20competitor%20to%20Netflix%2C%20while%20Netflix%20buying%20WBD%20would%20extend%20its%20dominance%20in%20streaming%20and%20give%20it%20more%20power%20to%20raise%20prices%20to%20consumers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%229ff3baee-dd6e-430c-99be-6b1b80906f5f%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ENetflix%20says%20its%20offer%20would%20be%20better%20for%20consumers%20and%20creators%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EFinancials%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Netflix%20said%20the%20deal%20would%20give%20it%20a%20number%20of%20financial