e%20three%20oil%20nations%20to%20help%20finance%20its%20bid%20for%20WBD%2C%20won't%20say.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20it%20sure%20seems%20like%20a%20question%20worth%20asking%2C%20as%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fparamount-wbd-warner-bros-discovery-bidding-war-hollywood-comcast-netflix-2025-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EParamount%20launches%20a%20hostile%20bid%20for%20WBD%3C%2Fa%3E%20after%20losing%20last%20week's%20auction%20to%20Netflix.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EParamount%20says%20the%20three%20petrostates%20will%20be%20part%20of%20the%20new%20bid%20%E2%80%94%20as%20they%20were%20in%20Paramount's%20previous%20offers%20for%20WBD%20(something%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsaudi-arabia-paramount-warner-bros-discovery-ellison-2025-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EParamount%20had%20at%20one%20point%20denied%3C%2Fa%3E).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20of%20a%20week%20ago%2C%20those%20three%20countries%20were%20going%20to%20kick%20in%20%2424%20billion%20%E2%80%94%20double%20the%20%2411.8%20billion%20the%20Ellison%20family%20planned%20to%20invest%20in%20WBD.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20Paramount%20won't%20say%20how%20much%20the%20three%20countries'%20sovereign%20wealth%20funds%20plan%20to%20invest%20in%20their%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.sec.gov%2FArchives%2Fedgar%2Fdata%2F2041610%2F000119312525310708%2Fd92876dex99a1a.htm%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Enewest%20proposal%3C%2Fa%3E.%20It%20says%20Larry%20and%20David%20Ellison%2C%20who%20currently%20own%20Paramount%2C%20along%20with%20RedBird%20Capital%2C%20the%20private%20equity%20group%2C%20will%20%26quot%3Bbackstop%26quot%3B%20the%20deal%20%E2%80%94%20meaning%20they%20promise%20to%20finance%20all%20of%20it%20if%20necessary.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20Paramount%20still%20anticipates%20those%20three%20countries%20will%20ultimately%20invest%20in%20a%20combined%20Paramount%2FWBD%2C%20along%20with%20Jared%20Kushner%20%E2%80%94%20Donald%20Trump's%20son-in-law%2C%20wh